法規內容.條文內容:
Organic agricultural products and in-conversion agricultural products with the containers or packaging shall be labelled with organic mark on each sold unit. However, a product which meets any of the following conditions is not allowed to be labelled with organic mark:
1. Imported organic agricultural products;
2. Imported organic agricultural products which have been packaged and certified domestically;
3. Organic processed agricultural products of which the imported organic ingredients account for over 50% and which have not been substantially transformed through processing domestically.
The specification and design of the organic mark are provided in the Appendix.
In-conversion agricultural products are not allowed to be labelled with organic mark.
